data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home nestled in a serene cul-de-sac in Eastern Alamance. Step into the spacious living room, where natural light floods in, creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxing or entertaining. The living room seamlessly transitions into the kitchen, featuring sleek black appliances and a stylish tile backsplash. The open layout ensures effortless flow throughout the main floor, where you'll also find a dining room and a convenient half bath for guests. Upstairs, the spacious owner suite boasts a vaulted ceiling, walk-in closet, and bathroom with a single sink vanity, makeup vanity, and a garden tub/shower combo. Two guest bedrooms share a hall bath, providing ample space for family or visitors. Situated in a great location with community amenities including a play area, this home offers the ideal combination of comfort, convenience, and community living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
